THE TRUTH MACHINE RECIEVES
THIS PROGRAM RECIEVES AN INPUT, IF THE INPUT IS ZERO,
IT PRINTS ZERO AND HALTS, IF THE INPUT IS NOT 0 THE MACHINE PRINTS ONE INDEFINITELY

NOTE: ALL OF MEMORY INITIALIZES WITH NOP WHICH IS 0x0

PROGRAM
 00 $JMM #20
 02 $LDS
 03 $CPZ
 04 $JEZ #30
 06 $NXT $INC
 08 $DSP $JMP #8 <- PRINTS ONE INDEFINITELY
~30 $JMM #80 <- RANDOM LOCATION
 32 $DSP
 33 $HALT